<i>noun</i>: 노출 [노출] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>노출 [노출]</dt><br>
<dd>1. exposure; disclosure; uncovering</dd><br>
<dd>감추어져 있는 것을 남이 보거나 알 수 있도록 겉으로 드러냄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of revealing something hidden to make it known or visible.</dd><br>
<dd>2. exposure</dd><br>
<dd>사진을 찍을 때 셔터를 열어 빛이 들어오게 하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of opening a shutter when taking a picture, to let light fall on the film.</dd><br>
<dd>3. exposure; influence</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 상황이나 환경의 영향을 직접 받게 하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of causing something to be directly influenced by a certain situation or environment.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>